<p>In this example, we demonstrate the the simplest way to connect to Ably and handle connection state events. See <a href="https://www.ably.io/documentation/realtime/connection">our Realtime Connection documentation</a> for more details.

<div class="row">
  <input id="connect" type="submit" value="Connect to Ably">
</div>

<div class="row" id="realtime-status"></div>
